quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  39,11,"Maaku: "Miin mi yamiraama dewugol Allah, la…ď…ďinana mo diina kan,"
  39,12,"Mi yamiraa kadi, gongol arano e jebbilii…ďe …ďeen"."
  39,13,"Maaku : "Miin mi…óo huli, si mi yeddii Joomi am, lepte √Ďalaande Mawnde"."
  39,14,"Maaku: "Ko Allah mi rewata, mi la…ď…ďinan mo diina am."
  39,15,"ndewee ko nji…óu…óon onon, hara wonaa KaŇčko. Maaku: "Ko woni hayru…ďe …ďen, ko …ďeen …ďe tawata √Ďande Darngal, …ďe hayrinii ko'e ma…ď…ďe, e …ďeynguureeji ma…ď…ďe". Nganndee ko nden woni hayrere …ďanngunde ndeen."
  39,16,"Hino woodirani …ďe seŇčgo dow ma…ď…ďe, kippoodi Yiite, e kippoodi senngo ley ma…ď…ďe. Ko …óum woni ko Allah hul…ďinirta jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen. Ko onon yo jiyaa…ďe Am, kori kulee Kam!"
  39,17,"∆Āeen wo…ó…óitor…ďe rewugol bewnooji …ói, …ďe nduttii e Allah, welo-welo no woodani …ďe. Wewlinir jiyaa…ďe am …ďeen,"
  39,18,"nanoo…ďe Konngol …ďeen, …ďe njokka ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e maggol. Ko …ďeen woni …ďe Allah feewni …ďen, ko …ďen ngoni joomiraa…ďe haqqille …ďeen."
  39,19,"E ko on mo konngol lepte jojji e mum... E ko aan da…óndata gon…óo ka Yiite?"
  39,20,"Si ko …ďen hul…ďe Joomi mun, hino woodani …ďe ku…ďeeje [ka Aljanna] e ku…ďeeje mahaa…óe dow majje, hara can…ói no ila ley majje. Ko fodoore Allah ! Allah non firtataa fodoore."
  39,21,"E a yiaani, won'de Allah saa∆īinirii ndiyam ka kammu, o naadi …óam e ndeer …ďulli ka leydi; refti o yaltinira …óam remuru seedundu noone, refti ndu …óay…óa, yi'aa hindu soy…ói; refti O wa…óa …óum ko muncaa. Pellet, wonii e …óuum, waaju, wonan'de joomiraa…ďe haqqille …ďeen."